----    ------     ------- Redasos
------------------------------------------------------------------

1.  Install Manjaro xfce
2.  open terminal         sudo pacman -Syu
3.  sudo pacman -S xmonad xmobar dmenu rofi
4.  reboot
5.  start sesion "xmonad"
6.  start dmenu (Alt-p)
7.  open terminal
8.  sudo pacman -S xmonad-contrib
9.  sudo localectl set-x11-keymap us,lt,ru pc105 "" grp:alt_shift_toggle
10.  download xmonad.hs and xmobarrc
11. open thunar go   home   and    (Ctrl-h)
12. copy xmonad.hs in .xmonad
13. go the .config and new aplication name xmobar
14. copy xmobarrc in .config/xmobar
15. open terminal    xmonad --recompile
16. reboot
     wi-fi setting open terminal     nmtui
   after udate   xmonad --recompile   !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
   after update no start  Ctrl+Alt+F2 OR F3    xmonad --recompile

